data.description: ***Open House - Sunday, December 17th from 1 PM - 3 PM***If you're looking for a beautiful one-story home in an idyllic community, then you've found it! Serene Live Oak community with all your amenities just a few minutes away. High ceilings and beautifully crafted arch ways lend to this home's uniqueness. Open and airy floor plan for easy entertaining with family and friends. Primary bedroom has charming built-ins to help you prepare for your day. Tired of those hot Texas summers? Well, you have an outdoor oasis waiting for you at the end of the day. Lounge by your pool and have a cold drink on your deck or patio as you watch the sunset. Need extra storage or a he/she shed? We've got one of those, too! Newly painted and a new roof, so that's one less thing to worry about. Easy access to I-35 and 1604, Forum shopping center, RAFB and Fort Sam Houston. This home has everything you need!
